{"tid":478491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[屈機] 躉船佬另類浪漫 萬元打造縮水躉船","createTime":"2017-11-24T06:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T09:19:15.000Z","uid":34701,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8982e52b10411a55fcdf02a372820fc23e5c9cd8","tid":478491,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"在70、80年代，香港是重要的轉口港，外國遠洋船到港，要靠躉船起卸貨物，這做法又稱「中流作業」。時至今日，躉船仍在運輸業中擔當重要角色，但其外表樸實，並非人人都識欣賞。偏偏有一名男子，數十年來獨愛躉船，近年更落手落腳，製作出多艘有齊控制室、起居室的「縮水躉船」，船上吊臂更可遙控吊起貨物。每個細節都做得鉅細無遺，他只希望讓大家知道：躉船都可以係藝術品！<br />\n<br />\n今年43歲的何榮泰(Kenny) ，生於水上人世家，因父母在油麻地經營躉船生意，自小便與家人一同在躉船居住，他形容躉船是他生命中一部分，「出世已經喺度住，由細到大所有嘢都係喺躉船上面做，有種情意結。」10來歲時，Kenny開始參與躉船工作，由駕駛、控制吊臂，以至接駁鋼線，船上每個崗位都要通曉。其後雖然轉行，但他對躉船的感情不減。3年前，終於下定決心，開始製作第一艘模型躉船。<br />\n<br />\n平日駕貨櫃車維生的Kenny，要犧牲休息時間，工餘時才可製作模型。遇上駁電、選購材料等問題，他要請教朋友，還有仍在經營躉船生意的兄長，「之前會跟阿哥去廣州、屯門船廠，去睇人哋點樣裝躉船，一路睇人整，一路用腦記住。」<span style=\"color: red;\">可以如此像真，全因Kenny對躉船有透徹了解，船上的每個角落，都瞭如指掌。他表示，平日製作不需繪畫圖則，在腦內構想躉船結構，「𠝹下剪下」就可完成。</span><br />\n<br />\n模型躉船依照真實躉船，主要以膠版製成，每艘重大約30公斤，需合二人之力才能抬起。船上有齊駕駛室、睡房、廁所、廚房，甚至是神台與神台燈，而模型吊臂可以轉動、上鈎和吊起假貨櫃，船身亦裝有LED小燈泡，可以着燈，「真船有嘅嘢，模型船度都可以搵到！」由於部分組件無法自製，需要送往廠房訂造，每艘船的成本需逾萬港元，製作時間亦需至少半年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d9F8wM4Ytq2guAWh8sH0aw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/dc1b5ded6cee3604c17bc06dc28c69c0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fd9F8wM4Ytq2guAWh8sH0aw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fdc1b5ded6cee3604c17bc06dc28c69c0&h=31a8ab6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出生於水上人世家、自小在躉船居住，Kenny對躉船有種情意結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rzT85elNIehHEEoeaT4k4g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/460311f84f82032ae46e99122934e2c7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrzT85elNIehHEEoeaT4k4g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F460311f84f82032ae46e99122934e2c7&h=f3add992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「吊鈎」亦是一絲不苟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RWQ8bwfM4t33vPRC7IkmoA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/fe3c522dbc40eea92ecee6ff6162d069\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRWQ8bwfM4t33vPRC7IkmoA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Ffe3c522dbc40eea92ecee6ff6162d069&h=a3c4cf1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n模型躉船的內部十分精細，房間、廁所、樓梯甚至神台燈都有做足。(受訪者提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/udvMf0w8N4glLZEbySk9fA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/86d282b2d934cf07d58a848e1f612cfb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FudvMf0w8N4glLZEbySk9fA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F86d282b2d934cf07d58a848e1f612cfb&h=92f77a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n模型吊臂可以<span style=\"color: red;\">遙控移動</span>，吊起迷你貨櫃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/bkn-20171124060040126-1124_00822_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171124%2Fbkn-20171124060040126-1124_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=SMktEMoWLNgn8ZGgHr2NV4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=87490b80\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/bkn-20171124060040126-1124_00822_001.html?refer=hn</a><br />\n<br />\n好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfa0f193fd1c08ce55170b4effc3a3a69cc9cf1","tid":478491,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3766038c6e0292e946b2aac826e15a010d0092b2","tid":478491,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"以為住係船唔使買樓"},{"pid":"8a2b8bfa4d5725edb91a29d1cad18333753cc157","tid":478491,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為住係船唔使買樓</blockquote><br />\n其實唔好住，好污 joe <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd9d0e990b34350a7d466675f9a9a98873a7092","tid":478491,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"我有錢都想買隻躉船住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7e1ee46347a9711b3d27cc16a9d38f8a786739","tid":478491,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以為住係船唔使買樓</blockquote><br />\n其實唔好住，好污 joe <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26498841eb07567829a16c5099ea07935bb934f","tid":478491,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"好有心機"},{"pid":"ce95595b2e28d5e683aa41f0371d28f2b1764985","tid":478491,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"男人浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e64bbd0f5a8766c55a422335ad647922b0d492","tid":478491,"uid":5